adviseScripts.text: Hey, Cutey!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Which do you like better: hot or cold?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Cold?
If you are going to do an experiment, tell me in advance. I hate both.
Oh, really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Okay. If you feel so strongly about it...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I'll take you to a cold chamber and see how you do!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Ha! That's just like you!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You catch on fast!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: That's what I like about you!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Maxwell while doing various tests.
My Cutey has been lookin' mighty fine lately.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: What do you think, Cutey? Is My Cutey missing anything?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Nothing at all, it's perfect.
It doesn't have any charm to it.
Are you just saying that to make me feel better?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I want you to tell me what you really think...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Well, thanks for the compliment anyway.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Yes. You're right.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: If you step back and take it all in, it's clearly lacking a sense of charm.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I'm glad I asked you! Thanks!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I chat with Maxwell while doing various tests.
There's a Nikke up in the North who destroys everything she touches.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: She's been damaging my poor little My Cuteys.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: What should I do?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You can't lose. You've got to find some way to best this Nikke.
If you want to cure a disease, you've got to eliminate the cause.
You're right! I can't lose!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I'll find a way to stop this Nikke from doing any more damage.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: And you're going to help me, aren't you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Eliminate the cause?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Sounds effective, but it doesn't seem very scientific...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Besides, Nikkes can't fight against other Nikkes.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Oh, I get it! You must have been making a joke! Very funny.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I chat with Maxwell while doing various tests.
I feel like Laplace's hero complex is worse than ever.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Do you think it has something to do with you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I think so.
I don't think so.
So it does have something to do with you, doesn't it?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I assume you did something to encourage her?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Fine. Do whatever you want, so long as you realize this is all your fault.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Hee hee! You sure about that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I heard you met with Laplace yesterday.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Well, okay.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You're adorable when you're clueless, Cutey.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Maxwell about Laplace.
Agh! I can't take this!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Drake's really been stressing me out lately.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Why in the world is she always in such a rush?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: How do you put up with her, Cutey?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I don't. She drives me up the wall as well.
She admits her faults, so I'm willing to cut her some slack.
Really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I thought for sure you would be able to handle it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Didn't see this coming at all!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I guess you're right.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: If that wasn't the case, she and I would have butted heads sooner.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: *Sigh*
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Either way, I'm glad you have a way of dealing with it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Maxwell about Drake.
Cutey, who do you think would win in a fight?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Matis or Absolute?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Matis.
Absolute.
Really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You're just trying to butter me up, aren't you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You know how much I love flattery.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Makes me happy to hear you say it, Cutey.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Are you serious?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You'd say that, even when it's a member of Matis asking the question?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Are you sure?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: All right, then. In order to defeat the oh-so-amazing Absolute,
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: you'll have to help me do some more testing on the My Cuteys.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Right?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Maxwell while doing various tests.
Do you like hot or cold food better?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: If this is some kind of test, then neither.
I'll eat whatever you give me.
Huh? This isn't a test at all.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Have a little more trust in me! Hee hee.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Aw, you're always so polite.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: We may end up spending a lot of time together in the future, you know?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Going on assignments, doing tests...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: That's why I'm trying to learn what you like beforehand.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I'll keep that in mind.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I spend some meaningful time with Maxwell.
Laplace says we are all heroes.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: But in my opinion, Drake is more of the villain type.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: As for me, I'm more like a researcher.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: What do you think, Cutey? Would I be a researcher working for the villains, or for the heroes?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You'd be working for the villains.
You'd be working for the heroes.
Oh? Do I give off a villainous vibe?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You're not completely off the mark.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I'm surprised to hear you say that. You think of me like a hero?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I'm... Well, I'm not sure if that makes me happy or sad.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Either way, Laplace is our leader, so we all have to act like heroes for the time being.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: We'll say you're correct... for now.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Maxwell about heroism.
Hey Cutey, do you have any unusual sleeping habits?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Tossing, turning...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: hitting the walls and floor, that kind of thing?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Yes.
No.
Really? Is that so...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: In that case, if I ever need to put you on anesthetics,
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I'll just have to use a stronger dose.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: No? Glad to hear it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: If I ever need to put you on anesthetics,
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I won't need to waste too much on you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: As I spend time with Maxwell, shivers run down my spine.
Cutey, who would you say is more difficult to deal with?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Mustang, or Syuen?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Syuen.
Mustang.
Ha ha! You hate Syuen that much?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I guess I can see it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Mustang seems easygoing on the outside,
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: but that's the kind of person you really have to watch out for.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: So, even though you're not a huge fan of Syuen, you don't find her overly difficult?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I feel the same way.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I think Syuen is much better than Mustang.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Syuen may have the occasional mean streak,
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: but at least it's the kind of mean that I can understand.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Maxwell about the CEOs of the Big Three.
If there was a button in front of you that would destroy the world,
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: would you press it?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Yes.
No.
Really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Apparently you don't have any strong attachment to this world.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I still have a lot that I want to research.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: No surprise there!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: After all, you have a grand vision of changing this world yourself.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: If this world was to end tomorrow, I'd be devastated.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: There's so much I still want to accomplish.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Maxell and I talk about the end of the world.
Hey Cutey, do you have a moment?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: For you, all the time in the world.
Sorry, can't spare a single second.
Perfect!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Let's go out to lunch.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Haha, you thought I was going to ask you to help me with an experiment, didn't you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Even then, you still said that you had time for me. You're the best!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Really? That's too bad.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I was going to ask if you wanted to get lunch.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You probably thought I was going to ask you to help me with an experiment, didn't you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Maxwell and I hash out what we're going to have for lunch.
Cutey, if something important came up and you couldn't get a hold of the other person, what would you do?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I would just keep trying until I could get in touch with them.
I would go find them.
Even if you're not sure when you'll be able to reach them?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You're more patient than me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I could never do that, I'd run out of patience almost straight away.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: That could work...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Once you found them, you could talk face-to-face.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: And you wouldn't have to wait.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Maxwell and I had a fun time talking to each other.
If we succeed in reclaiming the surface
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: and rid the world of all Raptures,
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: what do you think will happen to all the Nikkes?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: We'll all live a peaceful coexistence on the surface.
... I guess you'll all be scrapped.
That'd be great!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: That way you and I can continue our research, just like we are now.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I like the sound of that!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I doubt it would go that far.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: But, even if we're not scrapped, do you think they try and keep us hidden away?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: We'd be considered remnants of a violent past, obsolete weapons of war that are no longer necessary.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Maxwell and I speculate about potential futures.
I think I've been too focused on my research lately.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: My thoughts are all in a jumble.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: What do you do to clear your head?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Space out.
Do something that I enjoy.
Eh...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: When I space out, my thinking only gets more erratic.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: That sounds like a good idea.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: All right, it's settled then.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Come to the power plant later.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I spend time helping Maxwell organize her thoughts.
Why does Laplace insist on leaping through the window when there's a perfectly good door nearby?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: We could have constructed an entire building with all the money spent repairing broken windows.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: It's what heroes do apparently.
It's a bad habit she needs to fix.
Yeah, I guess just walking through the door isn't exactly a grand entrance.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Were you thinking that I'd say something like that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: It's because you always spoil her, so she does it so incessantly.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: It's fine to humor her, but don't go overboard.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Oh, I thought you were gonna let it slide. I totally didn't see that coming.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: That's great! If you keep letting her get away with it, who's going to foot the bill?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: How can we get her to stop leaping through windows...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I spend time with Maxwell fretting about all the windows Laplace has shattered.
I had a dream last night where I had achieved a historic breakthrough in my research.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: But the details are fuzzy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Does it really matter if you can't remember?
Try your best to remember.
Good point.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: It's only a dream, so I shouldn't waste time obsessing over it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Heck, it might be better that I can't remember it. That way I can get it out of my mind faster.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Our minds are in sync today, Cutey!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Nope, I'm drawing a blank.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Well, it was only a dream, so there's no point in obsessing over it. I'll succeed in real life.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Speaking of which, you and I can run some tests later.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Maxwell about research.
Nothing in the world can beat Missilis technology!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Wouldn't you say?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I think you're being arrogant.
I admire your confidence.
... I suppose you're right. They haven't even been able to exterminate the Raptures, and here I am saying they're the best in the world.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: All right then, best in the Ark.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: If you ask me though, it's not arrogance, but confidence.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: After all, how can you expect to unveil the secrets of our world without being ambitious?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Actually, that came off a little pompous as well, haha.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Do you really think that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You really know how to make people feel good about themselves.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: You're a real social butterfly as well.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I think that's a type of confidence as well.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Also, if you want to get discover more of the truths behind our world, you need unbridled ambition!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Maxwell about Missilis technology.
Hey, Cutey! Look outside.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Today's perfect for running some tests, don't you think?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: ...Sure.
No.
You say that, but your face says otherwise! Haha!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I'm just kidding. Besides, it's time for us to have a talk with each other.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Let's talk a bit more.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Wow, so adamant! Truly an immovable object.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Harsh!
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Just kidding! Anyway, let's keep talking.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Maxwell and I have a nice casual chat.
Have you ever thought about the future?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: What do you imagine life will be like then?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Probably still fighting with the Raptures, what else?
Hopefully we'll have reclaimed the surface.
I didn't think you'd have such a bleak outlook on the future.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: However, I have to say I feel the same way.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: We know so little about the Raptures, it would be foolish to entertain the idea of reclaiming the surface.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: With things as they are now, we'd need a miracle for that to happen.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: And unless it can be scientifically proven, I'm not one to believe in miracles.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: So you dream of a hopeful future?
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: I can't say the same for myself,
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: but if that's what you think, then that's what you think.
adviseScripts.speaker: Maxwell

adviseScripts.text: Maxwell and I discuss the future.
